{"text_id":100482,"tokens":["A"," novel"," method"," is"," proposed"," for"," evaluating"," the"," critical"," nucleus"," and"," surface"," tension"," in"," systems"," with"," first","-","order"," phase"," transitions","."," We"," have"," developed"," a"," hybrid"," approach"," combining"," the"," classical"," nucleation"," theory"," with"," the"," density"," functional"," theory"," (","DFT",")"," to"," describe"," the"," thermodynamic"," properties"," of"," the"," system","."," The"," key"," idea"," is"," to"," utilize"," the"," DFT"," to"," calculate"," the"," excess"," free"," energy"," associated"," with"," the"," formation"," of"," a"," nucleus",","," which"," is"," then"," used"," to"," determine"," the"," critical"," nucleus"," size"," and"," the"," surface"," tension","."," Our"," methodology"," involves"," a"," three","-","step"," procedure",":"," first",","," we"," compute"," the"," thermodynamic"," properties"," of"," the"," system"," using"," DFT",";"," second",","," we"," calculate"," the"," excess"," free"," energy"," of"," a"," nucleus"," using"," the"," computed"," thermodynamic"," properties",";"," and"," third",","," we"," determine"," the"," critical"," nucleus"," size"," and"," surface"," tension"," by"," minimizing"," the"," excess"," free"," energy"," with"," respect"," to"," the"," nucleus"," size","."," The"," results"," obtained"," demonstrate"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," our"," approach"," in"," accurately"," predicting"," the"," critical"," nucleus"," size"," and"," surface"," tension"," in"," a"," variety"," of"," systems"," with"," first","-","order"," phase"," transitions","."," The"," method"," offers"," a"," promising"," solution"," to"," the"," long","-","standing"," problem"," of"," evaluating"," the"," critical"," nucleus"," and"," surface"," tension"," in"," these"," systems",","," which"," has"," important"," implications"," for"," understanding"," and"," predicting"," the"," behavior"," of"," phase"," transitions"," in"," complex"," systems","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}